《'''睁开你的双眼'''》（{{lang-es|''''' Abre los ojos'''''}}；{{lang-en|'''''Open Your Eyes'''''}}）是一部1997年西班牙电影，由[[亚历杭德罗·阿梅纳瓦尔|亚历杭德罗·阿梅纳瓦尔]]执导。该片获[[东京电影节|东京电影节]]最佳影片、西班牙[[哥雅奖|哥雅奖]]最佳导演、最佳影片等奖项。影片的类型是剧情片、侦探片、科幻片、恐怖片的大杂烩。<ref>张栋等主编. 新青年DVD手册 精华版 第3辑. 北京市：新世界出版社, 2003.09. 页44.</ref>一些评论家把本片梦境与现实交织的主题与[[佩德罗·卡尔德隆·德·拉·巴尔卡|卡尔德隆]]的杰作《[[人生如梦|人生如梦]]》相联系。<ref>{{cite journal |author=[http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Perri%2c+Dennis-a11422 Perri, Dennis] |date=1 September 2008 |title=Amenabar's Abre los ojos: the posthuman subject |journal=Hispanofila |volume= |issue= |pages= |publisher=The Free Library |url=http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:5uWQFj11s2YJ:www.thefreelibrary.com/Amenabar's%2BAbre%2Blos%2Bojos:A%2Bthe%2Bposthuman%2Bsubject.-a0202311647+%22Abre+los+ojos%22%22La+vida+es+sueno%22+Amenabar+%22The+movie's+intersecting+planes+of+dream+and+reality+have+prompted+some+critics+to+suggest+comparisons+to+Calderon's+masterwork%22&hl=en |accessdate=19 July 2012 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Cine-Lit 2000. Essays on hispanic film and fiction |first=Sandra |last=Robertson |editors=Cabello-Castellet, George; Martí-Olivella, Jaume; Wood, Guy H. |year=2000 |publisher=[[Oregon_State_University|Oregon State University]] |location=[[Corvallis,_Oregon|Corvallis, Oregon]] |chapter=Life is Virtual Dream: Amenábar Reading Calderón (pp. 115-25) |isbn=0-96319273-6 |chapterurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=TxMIAQAAMAAJ&q=%22Life+is+Virtual+Dream:+Amenábar+Reading+Calderón%22 |accessdate=July 19, 2012 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=TxMIAQAAMAAJ |archive-date=2013-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231230144/http://books.google.com/books?id=TxMIAQAAMAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Teatro Calderoniano Sobre el Tablado. Calderón y Su Puesta en Escena a Través de Los Siglos |first=Jing |last=Xuan |editor1-first=Manfred |editor1-last=Tietz |year=2003 |publisher=[[Franz_Steiner_V